#: woocommerce-google-analytics-integration.php:143
msgid "Get detailed insights into your sales with Google Analytics Pro"
msgstr "Få detaljerede indsigt i dit salg med Google Analytics Pro"

#. translators: 1: href link to GA pro
#: woocommerce-google-analytics-integration.php:146
msgid "Add advanced tracking for your sales funnel, coupons and more. [<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a> &gt;]"
msgstr "Tilføj avanceret sporing til dit salg, dine kuponer med mere. [<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">Lær mere</a> &gt;] "

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:154
msgid "Enable this to find broken or dead links. An \"Event\" with category \"Error\" and action \"404 Not Found\" will be created in Google Analytics for each incoming pageview to a non-existing page. By setting up a \"Custom Goal\" for these events within Google Analytics you can find out where broken links originated from (the referrer). %sRead how to set up a goal%s."
msgstr "Aktiver dette at finde brudte eller døde links. En \"handling\" med kategori \"Fejl\" og handling \"404 Ikke Fundet\" vil blive oprettet i Google Analytics for hver indgående sidevisning til en ikke-eksisterende side. Ved at oprette et \"Brugertilpasset mål\" for disse handlinger inden for Google Analytics kan du finde ud af hvor brudte links stammer fra (henvisningssted). %sLæs hvordan man opsætter et mål%s."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:153
msgid "Track 404 (Not found) Errors."
msgstr "Spore 404 (Ikke Fundet) fejl."

#. Author URI of the plugin
msgid "https://woocommerce.com"
msgstr "https://woocommerce.com"

