#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:133
msgid "Set the Google Analytics code to support Enhanced Link Attribution. %sRead more about Enhanced Link Attribution%s."
msgstr "Indstil Google Analytics koden for understøttelse af forbedret Link tilskrivninger. %sLæs mere om forbedret Link tilskrivninger %s."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:132
msgid "Use Enhanced Link Attribution"
msgstr "Anvend udvidet link tilskrivninger"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:233
msgid "Please note, for transaction tracking to work properly, you will need to use a payment gateway that redirects the customer back to a WooCommerce order received/thank you page."
msgstr "Bemærk, for transaktions sporingen skal fungere korrekt, skal du anvende en betalings gateway som omdirigerer kunden tilbage til en WooCommerce ordre modtaget/takke side."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:230
msgid "Please allow Google Analytics 24 hours to start displaying results."
msgstr "Google Analytics behøver op til 24 timer til at begynde at vise resultater."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:217
msgid "Checkout Process Initiated"
msgstr "Købsprocessen indledt"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:209
msgid "Product Detail Views"
msgstr "Produkt detaljer visninger"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:201
msgid "Product Clicks from Listing Pages"
msgstr "Produkt klik fra liste sider"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:193
msgid "Product Impressions from Listing Pages"
msgstr "Produkt indtryk fra liste sider"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:185
msgid "Remove from Cart Events"
msgstr "Fjern fra varekurvs begivenheder"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:176
msgid "Enhanced eCommerce allows you to measure more user interactions with your store, including: product impressions, product detail views, starting the checkout process, adding cart items, and removing cart items. Universal Analytics must be enabled for Enhanced eCommerce to work. Before enabling this setting, turn on Enhanced eCommerce in your Google Analytics dashboard. <a href=\"%s\">See here for more information</a>."
msgstr "Udvidett e-handel gør det muligt at måle flere brugerinteraktioner med din butik, herunder: produkt indtryk, detaljer produktoversigt, start af købsprocessen, tilføj- og fjernelse af produkter i varekurv. Universal Analytics skal være aktiveret for at udvidet e-handel skal fungerer. Før du aktiverer denne indstilling, du aktivere Udvidet E-handel i din Google Analytics kontrolpanel. <a href=\"%s\">Se her for mere information</a>."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:175
msgid "Enable Enhanced eCommerce "
msgstr "Aktivere udvidet e-handel "

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:174
msgid "Enhanced eCommerce"
msgstr "Udvidet E-handel"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:167
msgid "Add to Cart Events"
msgstr "Læg i varekurv handling"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:161
msgid "This requires a payment gateway that redirects to the thank you/order received page after payment. Orders paid with gateways which do not do this will not be tracked."
msgstr "Dette kræver en betalings-gateway, der omdirigerer til siden tak/ordre modtaget efter betaling. Ordrer som betales med alm. gateways, vil ikke blive sporet."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:160
msgid "Purchase Transactions"
msgstr "Købs transaktioner"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:147
msgid "Enabling this option is mandatory in certain countries due to national privacy laws. %sRead more about IP Anonymization%s."
msgstr "Aktivering af denne indstilling er obligatorisk i visse lande på grund af nationale lovgivning ang. Privatlivs Politik. %sLæs mere om IP anonymisering %s."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:146
msgid "Anonymize IP addresses."
msgstr "Anonymisere IP-adresser."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:140
msgid "Uses Universal Analytics instead of Classic Google Analytics. If you have <strong>not</strong> previously used Google Analytics on this site, check this box. Otherwise, %sfollow step 1 of the Universal Analytics upgrade guide.%s Enabling this setting will take care of step 2. %sRead more about Universal Analytics%s. Universal Analytics must be enabled to enable enhanced eCommerce."
msgstr "Bruger Universel Analytics i stedet for klassiske Google Analytics. Hvis du <strong>ikke</strong> tidligere har anvendt Google Analytics på dette websted skal du markere dette afkrydsningsfelt. Ellers, %sfølg trin 1 af guiden om opgradering af Universel Analytics.%s Aktivere denne indstilling vil gå videre til trin 2. %sLæs mere om Universel Analytics%s. Universal Analytics skal være aktiveret til at aktivere udvidet e-handel."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:139
msgid "Enable Universal Analytics"
msgstr "Aktiver Universal Analytics"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:126
msgid "Set the Google Analytics code to support Display Advertising. %sRead more about Display Advertising%s."
msgstr "Sæt Google Analytics-kode til at understøtte Vis Reklamer. %sLæs mere om Vis Reklamer%s."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:125
msgid "\"Display Advertising\" Support"
msgstr "\"Vis Reklamer\" Support"

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:119
msgid "This tracks session data such as demographics, system, etc. You don't need to enable this if you are using a 3rd party Google analytics plugin."
msgstr "Dette spore sessionsdata som demografi, system, osv. Du behøver ikke at aktivere denne hvis du bruger en 3rd part Google analytics plugin."

#: includes/class-wc-google-analytics.php:118
msgid "Enable Standard Tracking"
msgstr "Aktiver Standard Sporing"

